PrecisAmendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 816 permitting the use of Polysorbate 80 as an emulsifier/stabilizer in annatto and turmeric colour formulations thus providing improved acid and shelf stability of these colours which are used in a variety of products.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1991-0710 Publication Date: 1991-12-18
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS Schedule No. 816 permitting the
use of Polysorbate 80 as an emulsifier/stabilizer in annatto and turmeric
colour formulations thus providing improved acid and shelf stability of
these colours which are used in a variety of products.
